Comment: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.16,Title,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------ TEXT ------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小樱小姐真是气势汹汹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是 好能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然是为了给上次的事赔罪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一顿看来是要不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鸟子 你还吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小樱的赔礼会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.66,0:00:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来是我和空鱼的和好会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和 和好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛豆 土豆沙拉 凉拌番茄 烤串五根拼盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炸鸡块 生拌马肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裙带菜银鱼干白萝卜沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有 炙烤醋青花鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼呢 你点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就先这些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的 我收拾一下空碟子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你点了那么多 是打算吃完的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总会有办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们有两个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久等了 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前从里世界回来的时候捡的帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个在空鱼眼里是有点奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我记得那时候它隐约散发着银光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么来历不明的东西 你居然还敢戴头上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}适合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鸟子戴什么都会好看的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行啦 吃饭的时候摘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们下次什么时候去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次 鸟子你就不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前 我和鸟子差点就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 但是我们还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害怕啊 但是不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是只有我一个 早就吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在吓坏之前说不定就已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是也害怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那为什么还要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总会有办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们有两个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}问题是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀 这是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 是账单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼啊 多少钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一万九千零八日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一万九千
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然到这个数了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小樱小姐也吃了不少的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那部分另外算呗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能这样的吗 话说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没事吧 能自己回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Probably Maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海军陆战队的训练也没问题 倒也不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 你好 那个 我们要买单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先回去的人那部分能帮我们另外算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}“久比里矢来野手 阿部拉加良素来了”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}“阿部拉加良素来了”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你听懂他刚才说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没注意听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你刚才是不是汪了一声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼 车站往哪走来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边啦 你清醒点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不觉得有点暗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是在节电啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不用搞得这么暗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}车站有这么远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼 你走错路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又把责任推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说 池袋有这么乡下的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是里世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鸟子 你来过晚上的异世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为冴月说 晚上很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼 你带枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能带
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁会带着枪来喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道你带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我正在想 早知道就带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么会到里世界来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离开店面的时候 是感觉眼前晃了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 在那之前好像就不太对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道那家店就是里世界入口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前去了那么多次都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没在店里做什么奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}八尺大人的帽子 我戴了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都叫你别戴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也 也不一定就是因为这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你刚才都说了“就是那个”了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个可能性还挺高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那 我再戴一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 不行 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别碰它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 好啦 我不碰 OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 先不要随便走动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}万一踩到异错就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得大概是做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是 尸体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是什么 先逃吧 跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼 跑这么快 不用担心异错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟着我 千万别离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上坡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还挺陡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鸟子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别停下 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}砂石地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看见什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前面也许有车站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要放弃 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总会有办法的啦 我们有两个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空鱼 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}千万别抬头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别 别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.27,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中尉 那东西还在那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.27,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hey lieutanent. That thing's still out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.64,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.64,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.56,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.56,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are they really human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.43,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们会不会也是怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.43,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They could be one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.14,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中尉 不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.14,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Lieutanent! Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.42,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们一定也是野生物  杀了她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.42,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They gotta be “Wild things”. Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.57,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷静  古雷格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.57,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Stand dowm, Greg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.66,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也看见她们被“角男（Horn man）”追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.66,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You saw them being chased by the Horn Man too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.04,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.04,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They are humen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.29,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.29,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.92,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是命令  士官长  把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.92,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is a order, Master Sergeant. Lower your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.55,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.55,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们是什么人 从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东京的  池袋 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.01,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.01,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Tokyo？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:20.97,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是说东京吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:20.97,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Did she said Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.02,双语,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可是几百英里外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.02,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's hundreds miles from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们从哪里来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 你们是驻日美军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是海军陆战队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是查理连队 12 苍马大队中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威尔·德雷克中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 你们也不知道出口在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们甚至不知道是因为什么才误入了异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还以为终于有机会离开这个地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们可能也没法帮助你们回到原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们来到“另一侧”已经有一个多月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依然没有找到逃出方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们是怎么来到这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们本来在山中训练
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何时 整支部队就都来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}发现这里的植被和冲绳不同时 已经来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们重整四散的中队 以车站为据点筑起阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但还是出现了牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}牺牲者 是被刚才的怪物杀掉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那只是其中一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们看见那些吊在怪物腹部的尸体了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是我们的战友 也包括那只骡子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}“骡子” 是那只像长颈鹿的无头怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它本是随军行动的运输机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在搬运遗体时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然踩到奇怪的捕熊陷阱  就再也动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时我们只能把它丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后它就变成那副模样出现 开始袭击人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}“捕熊陷阱” 是说异错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那吱吱声原来是马达声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然对机械也有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你刚才说有车站
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCronosPro-SubhIt\fs55\b1\pos(960,978)\blur3}Station February
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二月车站
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是个小而破旧的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCronosPro-SubhIt\fs55\b1\pos(960,978)\blur3}February
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二月 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么叫“二月”?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面就是这样写的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是车站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里有通电吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来的时候就已经亮着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但并没有找到通向外部的电线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有其他废弃车站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}目前我们尚未发现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 这里似乎不是废弃车站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶  意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnCronosPro-SubhIt\fs55\b1\pos(960,978)\blur3}Station February
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二月车站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如月车站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来是没有时间让我们圣地巡礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那俩人好像失踪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天我代班 来讲讲人感受到恐惧的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先简单讲个一小时的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么 空鱼她们来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-故障 陷阱 可能是安全的\N-意义不明的自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么啊 是恶作剧电话啊
